description: Learn how to make pork dumplings with this tasty recipe. Create a dumpling making production line, and make it a fun activity for the whole family.
name: Pork Dumplings Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bring a large saucepan or wok of water to the boil. Line a large bamboo steamer with baking paper. Steam dumplings in 4 batches for 8 minutes or until cooked through. Serve with extra soy and green onion tops.
